{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0d7caf1b6a","title":"北京市公安局在清理积案中关于量刑标准的初步意见（节录）","origin":"《取缔反动会道门工作历史资料汇编（1948－1992年）》，公安部一局编印， 2009年。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8b8f2a5a40","index":0,"year":1951,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"0d7caf1b6a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"88473859d0","type":"title","text":"北京市公安局在清理积案中关于量刑标准的初步意见（节录）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0d7caf1b6a"},{"id":"1c64003cf9","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中华人民共和国惩治反革命条例之精神，结合北京的具体情况，在清理积案中关于量刑标准，拟制初步意见：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0d7caf1b6a"},{"id":"13dab3432e","type":"paragraph","text":"第一，依据惩治反革命条例第二条之规定，犯下列各种罪行之一者，处死刑。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0d7caf1b6a"},{"id":"7a4073b393","type":"appellation","text":"……","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0d7caf1b6a"},{"id":"e9e9604f88","type":"paragraph","text":"丁、反动道门首领：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0d7caf1b6a"},{"id":"d2ba02e2f4","type":"paragraph","text":"1.依靠反动道门势力，迫害人民群众致人于死者。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0d7caf1b6a"},{"id":"8ebac719c4","type":"paragraph","text":"2.利用反动道门，制造散布谣言，阴谋武装暴乱，图谋颠覆人民政权者。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0d7caf1b6a"},{"id":"2fded54ed1","type":"paragraph","text":"3.籍反动道门之权势，对人民群众进行愚弄、诱骗、敲诈、勒索、虐待、强奸、霸占等各种毒害手段，致使被害群众惨遭家破人亡，为人民群众极端痛恨的重要分子。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0d7caf1b6a"},{"id":"a3fe0731e2","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0d7caf1b6a"},{"id":"8200822dc6","type":"paragraph","text":"第三、凡具有下列条件之一者，经多数群众同意后，可释放或取保释放。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0d7caf1b6a"},{"id":"df45e89f4b","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0d7caf1b6a"},{"id":"8dec3d95e5","type":"paragraph","text":"巳、参加反动帮派道会门，经查确属一般徒众或基于迷信入道，无反革命活动者，在政府公布取缔后，已脱离组织，或现在真心悔过者。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0d7caf1b6a"},{"id":"425126b8b5","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0d7caf1b6a"}],"page":{"id":"96bf15b716","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0d7caf1b6a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}